<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Success Plan Coverage by CSM</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #16a34a;
    --red: #dc2626;
    --track: #e5e7eb;
    --ink: #1a1a2e;
    --muted: #6b7280;
    --border: #e5e7eb;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 32px;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size: 23px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  thead th {
    text-align: left; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; padding: 0 12px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  td { padding: 12px; vertical-align: middle; }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
  .name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
  .num { color: #4b5563; font-size: 13px; }
  .barcell { width: 280px; }
  .track { background: var(--track); border-radius: 4px; height: 14px; width: 240px; position: relative; }
  .fill { background: var(--green); border-radius: 4px; height: 14px; }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 11px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
  .pill.ok { background: var(--green); }
  .pill.gap { background: var(--red); }
  tr.gap { background: #fef2f2; }
  tr.gap .num { color: var(--red); font-weight: 700; }
  .divider td { padding: 4px 0; }
  .divider hr { border: none; border-top: 1px dashed var(--border); margin: 0; }
  .callout {
    margin-top: 26px; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
    background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .callout .dot {
    flex: 0 0 22px; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--red); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .callout .head { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .callout .body { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <h1>Success Plan Coverage by CSM</h1>
  <p class="sub">9 CSMs hold accounts — <strong>2 have zero Success Plans</strong> across their entire book of business.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>CSM</th><th>Accounts</th><th>Success Plans</th><th>Status</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="name">Sally McField</td><td class="num">59</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:240px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">31 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Ally Garcia</td><td class="num">35</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:23px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">3 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Latisha Jones</td><td class="num">29</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:16px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">2 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Katherine Bennett</td><td class="num">25</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:23px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">3 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Phillip Miller</td><td class="num">25</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:31px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">4 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Jared Nunes</td><td class="num">1</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:8px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">1 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td class="name">Cooper Consumption</td><td class="num">1</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:8px"></div></div></td><td><span class="pill ok">1 · Covered</span></td></tr>
      <tr class="divider"><td colspan="4"><hr></td></tr>
      <tr class="gap"><td class="name">Oscar Larson</td><td class="num">6</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"></div></td><td><span class="pill gap">0 · No Plans</span></td></tr>
      <tr class="gap"><td class="name">Yianno Kouletsis</td><td class="num">1</td><td class="barcell"><div class="track"></div></td><td><span class="pill gap">0 · No Plans</span></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="callout">
    <div class="dot">!</div>
    <div>
      <div class="head">2 CSMs have no Success Plans on any account</div>
      <div class="body">Oscar Larson (6 accounts) and Yianno Kouletsis (1 account) — a combined 7 accounts with zero plan coverage. Note: success-plan counts are tallied by each account's assigned CSM, not by plan owner.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
